Package net.newbiehacker.commodorej

Class Summary
Channel This class represents a channel on the server
ChannelListEntry This class represents an entry in a channel list (such as the ban list or the except list)
ConnectionManager The ConnectionManager allows creations of sessions to a server and ways to manipulate them.
Misc This class contains miscellaneous methods which were designed for use by the library
MiscNode This class represents a node which is not a channel or a user (could possibly be the server)
Node Represents a node, which is an object to which messages can be sent/received from
Session This class represents a connection to an IRC server with methods for obtaining information on the channels we're currently on and the users we've seen, etc.
User This class represents a user on IRC
 

Enum Summary
Node.Type The Type of this Node
